          //               '<div>The weather in Dubai is still forecast for rain on Friday 27 January, which could cause travel disruptions to your journey to campus.</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>Classes are currently scheduled to run as normal tomorrow, but students are advised to review the weather forecast on official channels regularly and make their own decision about whether they wish to travel to campus tomorrow. Your safety is our utmost priority.</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>If you use public transport or drive, please check on the official RTA channels for the latest travel updates.</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>The Student Transportation Service may also experience some disruption due to the weather. Please contact <a style="color:rgb(11, 96, 201) !important;" href="mailto:transport@mdx.ac.ae">transport@mdx.ac.ae</a> or your driver for updates and any questions.</div>',
